               <msContents>
                  <summary>Order of Chanting the Yarǝd Hymns, ሥርዓተ፡ አቋቋም፡, in Amharic</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="25v" facs="002">Fols 1r–25v</locus>
                     <title>Order of Chanting the Yarǝd Hymns, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሥርዓተ፡ አቋቋም፡</foreign></title>
                     <textLang mainLang="am">Amharic</textLang>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="10v" facs="002">Fols 1r–10v</locus>
                     <title>General Order of the Chanting</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> በሰላመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ንጽሕፍ፡ ነገረ፡ አዋጅ፡ ዘአቋቋም፡ በምልክት፡ በስም፡ አንድ፡ የሚሆኑ፡ አሉ፡ በዜማ፡ እየራሳቸው፡ ሆነው፡ በዝማሜ፡ በመረግድ፡ በጽፋት፡ ፩ የሚሆኑ፡ አሉ፡ . . .</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                     <locus from="10v" to="14r" facs="012">Fols 10v–14r</locus>
                     <title>Order of the ‘Ǝzǝl Chant, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሥርዓተ፡ ዕዝል፡ ዘዓቋቋም፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">‎ንዌጥን፡ በርድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔ[ር]፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ዕዝል፡ ዘአቋቋም፡ ‎‎ውእቱኬ፡ ዙር፡ ወለቡ፡ ፀወንየ፡ ፩ ናቸው፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                     <locus from="14r" to="17v" facs="015">Fols 14r–17v</locus>
                     <title>Order of the ‘Ǝraray Chant, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሥርዓተ፡ ዓራራይ፡ ዘዓቋቋም፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">እጽሕፍ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ዓራራይ፡ ዘዓቋቋም፡ ፀወንየ፡ ጽጌ፡ እስተርአየ፡ ሰላም፡ ለኪ፡ ዘድጓ፡ ሀገረ፡ ኢየሩሳሌም፡ እንዲል፡ ፩ ናቸው።</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                     <locus from="17v" to="18r" facs="019">Fols 17v–18r</locus>
                     <title>Order of the Ṣǝfat and Märägd Rhythms of Chanting, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሥርዓተ፡ ጽፋት፡ ወመረግድ፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ንጽሕፍ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ጽፋት፡ ወመረግድ፡ ለጊዜ፡ ዝናም፡ በሐ፡ ንበላ፡ ይሠብር፡ ማኅሌት፡ ድርሰ፡ ሲይከተላቸው፡ ወይወውዑ፡ ይሆናሉ፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
                     <locus from="18v" to="24v" facs="020">Fols 18v–24v</locus>
                     <title>Order of the Exchange of the  ‘Ǝraray and Gǝ`ǝz Modes, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተወላጦሙ፡ ለግዕዝ፡ ወለአራራይ፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ናሁ፡ ወጠንኩ፡ ጽሒፈ፡ ተወላጦሙ፡ ለግዕዝ፡ ወለአራራይ፡ ዘወጽአ፡ እምጐንደር፡ ወዝንቱ፡ ጥበብ፡ ዘይከሠተ፡ ኅቡረ፡ ወያበርህ፡ ልበ፡ . . .</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6">
                     <locus from="24v" to="25r" facs="026">Fols 24v–25r</locus>
                     <title>Order of the Wazema (Ceremony on the Eve of a Festival) Chant, <foreign xml:lang="gez">አደራረስ፡ ዘዋዜማ፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7">
                     <locus from="25r" to="25v" facs="026">Fols 25r–25v</locus>
                     <title>Order of Chanting the Image, <foreign xml:lang="gez">አደራረስ፡ ዘመልክእ፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.8">
                     <locus from="25v" to="25v" facs="027">Fols 25v–25v</locus>
                     <title>Order for Chanting the Gǝ`ǝz Poem of Wazema, <foreign xml:lang="gez">አደራረስ፡ ዘቅኔ፡ ዋዜማ፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                  </msItem>

                </msItem>

               </msContents>
